# Keep the Docker build context minimal and free of local/private state.
# The Dockerfiles use explicit COPY of source dirs and regenerate web assets
# (npm ci + vite build) and Go binaries inside the build, so build outputs,
# dependencies, local runtime state, and AI/editor files are all excluded here.

### Version control and CI metadata
.git
.gitignore
.github

### Local AI agent guidance and session state
AGENTS.md
CLAUDE.md
todo.md
codex-input.md
.claude
.sideplane

### OS / editor files
.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini
.vscode
.idea
*.iml

### Environment and local secrets
.env
.env.*
*.local
*.secret
*.secrets

### Certificates and keys
*.pem
*.key
*.crt
*.csr
*.p12
*.pfx

### Go build output and tool state
bin/
dist/
build/
coverage.out
*.test
*.prof
*.pprof
go.work
go.work.sum

### Node / frontend dependencies and build output
node_modules
web/node_modules
.npm
.pnpm-store
.yarn
web/dist
web/build
web/.vite
web/coverage
web/prototype
*.tsbuildinfo

### Frontend test artifacts
web/playwright-report
web/test-results
web/tests

